ss=\"n\">ext</span> <span class=\"n\">y</span><span class=\"bp\">;</span> <span class=\"n\">exact</span> <span class=\"o\">‚ü®</span><span class=\"bp\">Œª</span> <span class=\"o\">‚ü®‚ü®</span><span class=\"n\">_</span><span class=\"o\">,</span> <span class=\"n\">_</span><span class=\"o\">‚ü©,</span> <span class=\"n\">h</span><span class=\"o\">,</span> <span class=\"n\">rfl</span><span class=\"o\">‚ü©,</span> <span class=\"n\">h</span><span class=\"o\">,</span> <span class=\"bp\">Œª</span> <span class=\"n\">h</span><span class=\"o\">,</span> <span class=\"o\">‚ü®‚ü®</span><span class=\"n\">_</span><span class=\"o\">,</span> <span class=\"n\">x.2</span> <span class=\"n\">h</span><span class=\"o\">‚ü©,</span> <span class=\"n\">h</span><span class=\"o\">,</span> <span class=\"n\">rfl</span><span class=\"o\">‚ü©‚ü©,</span>\n <span class=\"bp\">Œª</span> <span class=\"n\">x</span><span class=\"o\">,</span> <span class=\"kd\">by</span> <span class=\"n\">ext</span><span class=\"bp\">;</span> <span class=\"n\">simp</span><span class=\"o\">‚ü©</span>\n\n<span class=\"kd\">example</span> <span class=\"o\">{</span><span class=\"n\">Œ±</span><span class=\"o\">}</span> <span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">S</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"n\">set</span> <span class=\"n\">Œ±</span><span class=\"o\">)</span> <span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">f</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"n\">S</span> <span class=\"bp\">‚Üí</span> <span class=\"bp\">ùí´</span> <span class=\"n\">S</span><span class=\"o\">)</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"bp\">¬¨</span> <span class=\"n\">function.surjective</span> <span class=\"n\">f</span> <span class=\"o\">:=</span>\n<span class=\"n\">mt</span> <span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">equiv.surjective</span> <span class=\"n\">_</span><span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">comp</span> <span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">function.cantor_surjective</span> <span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">equiv.set.powerset</span> <span class=\"n\">S</span> <span class=\"bp\">‚àò</span> <span class=\"n\">f</span><span class=\"o\">))</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n\n</div></div>",
